snippet.title: Romancing SaGa 3 (Released) Japanese Commercial
snippet.description:
If you're the sole survivor of the 300 year solar eclipse in Romancing Saga 3, you've been selected as the Child of Destiny. Visit chrislovesjapan.com for more content.
Raw video taken from the "Aya-Maya Eve" channel.

My transcription of the audio:
君だけの物語を作れ
ロマンシング サ・ガ3
スクウェア
